ロア対応-300x275.jpg 300w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_フロア対応-1024x940.jpg 1024w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_フロア対応-768x705.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1493px) 100vw, 1493px\" />              </div>\n              <div class=\"grid\">\n                <p>当社の送迎職員は、利用者様の安全と快適な移動をサポートする「懸け橋」として重要な役割を担っています。<br />\r\n丁寧な対応と安全運転で、利用者様に安心をお届けします！<br />\r\n送迎職員の一日のスケジュールをご紹介いたします（※細かな時間などは事業所や状況によって変わります）。</p>\n                              </div>\n            </div>\n                                      <div>\n                                  <div class=\"row02\">\n                    <div class=\"grid\">\n                      <p><p><b>午前の流れ</b></p><br />\r\n<b>7:45 出社</b><br />\r\n事業所に出勤し、一日の準備を開始します。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>7:50 送迎ミーティング</b><br />\r\n本日の欠席・振替・体験利用者を確認し、送迎割振やスケジュールをチェック。チームで情報を共有します。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>8:00 車両準備・安全確認</b><br />\r\n内外装等を点検、清掃や消臭も行い、快適な車内環境を整え、出発準備を行います。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid\">\n                      <img width=\"2560\" height=\"1811\" src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/★IMG_0679_2-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/★IMG_0679_2-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/★IMG_0679_2-300x212.jpg 300w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/★IMG_0679_2-1024x724.jpg 1024w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/★IMG_0679_2-768x543.jpg 768w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/★IMG_0679_2-1536x1087.jpg 1536w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/★IMG_0679_2-2048x1449.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                                  <div class=\"row02\">\n                    <div class=\"grid\">\n                      <p><b>8:10 迎え出発 ～ 利用者様宅へ出発</b><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>9:35 事業所到着 ～ 利用者様をご案内</b><br />\r\n施設に到着後、利用者様を安全に施設内へご案内。<br />\r\n足台の準備や段差の注意喚起を行い、丁寧に対応します。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>9:50 送迎車点検・駐車</b><br />\r\n車両を所定の位置に駐車し、走行距離や忘れ物の有無、内外装の確認を記録。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid\">\n                      <img width=\"1890\" height=\"1360\" src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_フロア対応（声掛け）.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_フロア対応（声掛け）.jpg 1890w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_フロア対応（声掛け）-300x216.jpg 300w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_フロア対応（声掛け）-1024x737.jpg 1024w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_フロア対応（声掛け）-768x553.jpg 768w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_フロア対応（声掛け）-1536x1105.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1890px) 100vw, 1890px\" />                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                                  <div class=\"row02\">\n                    <div class=\"grid\">\n                      <p><b>10:05 フロア見守り～休憩（30分）</b><br />\r\n事業所内で利用者様の見守り業務をサポート。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>11:00 送り出発 ～ 利用者様を自宅へお送り</b></p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid\">\n                      <img width=\"1711\" height=\"1540\" src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_降車介助.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_降車介助.jpg 1711w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_降車介助-300x270.jpg 300w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_降車介助-1024x922.jpg 1024w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_降車介助-768x691.jpg 768w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_降車介助-1536x1382.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1711px) 100vw, 1711px\" />                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                                  <div class=\"row02\">\n                    <div class=\"grid\">\n                      <p><b>12:40 送迎車点検・駐車</b><br />\r\n事業所に戻り、フロアの清掃や片付けをサポート。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n同様の流れで午後の利用者様の送迎を行います。<br />\r\n最終的に送迎車両、フロアの掃除を終え、次の日の準備が出来たら終業です！</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid\">\n                      <img width=\"1713\" height=\"1452\" src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_職員揃い.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_職員揃い.jpg 1713w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_職員揃い-300x254.jpg 300w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_職員揃い-1024x868.jpg 1024w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_職員揃い-768x651.jpg 768w, https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/送迎職員_職員揃い-1536x1302.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1713px) 100vw, 1713px\" />                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                              </div>\n                      </div>\n          </section>\n\n\n\n\n\n          \n\n\n\n\n                                                  <section class=\"page-section\">\n            <header class=\"heading02 u-mb0\">\n              <h2 class=\"heading02__text\">介護・送迎職員　<span class=\"is-black\">の求人</span></h2>\n            </header>\n            <div class=\"page-section__content\">\n                              <ul class=\"recinfos-list\">\n                                      <li class=\"recinfos-list__item\">\n                      <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruitment_info/1316/\" class=\"recinfos-list__link\">\n                                                  <span class=\"recinfos-list__status\">\n                            正                          </span>\n                                                <div class=\"recinfos-list__block\">\n                                                    <span class=\"recinfos-list__title\">介護・送迎職員</span>\n                        </div>\n                      </a>\n                    </li>\n                                  </ul>\n                          </div>\n          </section>\n          <div class=\"recruit-more container-out\">\n  <p class=\"recruit-more__head\">\n    採用について<br>\n    もっと見てみる\n  </p>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"recruit-more__content\">\n      <div class=\"recruit-more__block jobs\">\n        <h3 class=\"recruit-more__heading\">職種紹介</h3>\n        <p>まごころでは、デイサービスや訪問看護など複数の業態があり、様々な職種の方が活躍しています。</p>\n        <ul class=\"recruit-more-list\">\n                      <li class=\"recruit-more-list__item\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruit_profession/transportation-staff/#anchor\" class=\"recruit-more-list__link\">介護・送迎職員</a>\n            </li>\n                      <li class=\"recruit-more-list__item\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruit_profession/day_nurse/#anchor\" class=\"recruit-more-list__link\">デイサービスの看護師</a>\n            </li>\n                      <li class=\"recruit-more-list__item\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruit_profession/life-counselor/#anchor\" class=\"recruit-more-list__link\">生活相談員</a>\n            </li>\n                      <li class=\"recruit-more-list__item\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruit_profession/functional-training-instructor/#anchor\" class=\"recruit-more-list__link\">理学療法士・柔道整復師・鍼灸師</a>\n            </li>\n                      <li class=\"recruit-more-list__item\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruit_profession/visiting-nurse/#anchor\" class=\"recruit-more-list__link\">訪問看護師</a>\n            </li>\n                      <li class=\"recruit-more-list__item\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruit_profession/care-manager/#anchor\" class=\"recruit-more-list__link\">ケアマネージャー</a>\n            </li>\n                  </ul>\n        <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruit_profession/\" class=\"recruit-more__link u-fonten\">\n          VIEW ALL\n        </a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"recruit-more__block recruit\">\n        <h3 class=\"recruit-more__heading\">求人情報</h3>\n        <p>複数の職種と勤務地から選べます。ご不明点はお気軽にお問い合わせください。</p>\n        <ul class=\"recruit-more-list\">\n                      <li class=\"recruit-more-list__item\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruitment_info/1347/#anchor\" class=\"recruit-more-list__link\">理学療法士</a>\n            </li>\n                      <li class=\"recruit-more-list__item\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruitment_info/1247/#anchor\" class=\"recruit-more-list__link\">柔道整復師</a>\n            </li>\n                      <li class=\"recruit-more-list__item\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruitment_info/1316/#anchor\" class=\"recruit-more-list__link\">介護・送迎職員</a>\n            </li>\n                      <li class=\"recruit-more-list__item\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruitment_info/1261/#anchor\" class=\"recruit-more-list__link\">デイサービスの看護師</a>\n            </li>\n                  </ul>\n        <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruitment_info/\" class=\"recruit-more__link u-fonten\">\n          VIEW MORE\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div><div id=\"entry\" class=\"anchor-target\">\n  <div  class=\"entry-box\">\n    <!-- <img src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/themes/magokoro-theme/images/recruit/top/top_text_Joinus.png\" class=\"rectop-txt\"> -->\n    <p>まごころで、<br class=\"hide-pc\">一緒に働いてみませんか。</p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruit/\">採用トップへ</a>\n  </div>\n</div>          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n          <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <header class=\"heading u-center\">\n          <p class=\"heading__subtext u-fonten\">CONTACT</p>\n          <h2 class=\"heading__text\">お問い合わせ</h2>\n        </header>\n        <p class=\"u-pc-center\">\n          デイサービスのことや自宅介護の始め方など、お役に立てることがあれば<br class=\"sp-hide\">ぜひご相談ください。まごころがお手伝いさせていただきます。\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"contact-content\">\n          <p class=\"contact-text is-orange\">お気軽にお問い合わせください</p>\n          <div class=\"contact-btns\">\n            <div class=\"sp-hide\">\n              <span class=\"contact-btn contact-btn--tel\">\n                <span class=\"u-fonten\">011-613-3579</span>\n                <span>（ 代表 ）</span>\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sp-show\">\n              <a href=\"tel:011-613-3579\" class=\"contact-btn contact-btn--tel\">\n                <span class=\"u-fonten\">011-613-3579</span>\n                <span>（ 代表 ）</span>\n              </a>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/contact/\" class=\"contact-btn contact-btn--mail\">\n              お問い合わせ\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    </div>\n    <!-- /.l-contents -->\n    </div>\n    <!-- /.page-wrap -->\n    <footer class=\"l-footer\">\n      <div class=\"l-footer__inner\">\n        <div class=\"footer-info\">\n          <div class=\"footer-info-sitename\">\n            <p class=\"footer-info-sitename__message\"><span>聞く</span><span>見る</span><span>想う</span></p>\n            <img src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/logo.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"footer-info-sitename__logo\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"footer-info-access\">\n            <div class=\"inner\">\n              <p class=\"fo